# Trap the Sphero!

A fun and interactive game where users strategically place orange obstacles on a 5x5 grid to trap a Sphero robot. The Sphero can move horizontally or vertically, one space per turn, making it a challenging game of strategy and pathfinding!

---

## Prerequisites

To run this project, ensure the following are installed on your system:

- **Python 3.x**  
- **pip** (Python package manager)

---

## Installation Instructions

1. Clone this repository:  
    git clone <this repo url>
    cd <your project folder>
    pip install -r requirements.txt


